3) Dodge from 75 to 200 <br />
4) Invis Spell if they want to give me invis I want the damn spell not a song<br />
5) Undead Nuke see above - - - <br />
6) Parry AA - cost 2/4/6 for the following caps of 50/100/200 skill<br />
